{"tid":607252,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[洪非凡?］保皇狗打手關愛座hunter分身操作手法曝光","createTime":"2018-03-27T06:51:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-30T06:34:12.000Z","uid":38523,"like":20,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"2fb9316bbbbd227d836ac21d43f69d633e27f540","tid":607252,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T06:51:12.000Z","msg":"原貼又轉左去站務台<br />\n<a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/593908/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/593908/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/601006/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/601006/page/1</a><br />\n關狗扮捉五毛就大家都知<br />\n補選時一直屌泛民 放生保皇狗比人踢爆<br />\n一直轉移視線<br />\n之後反對佢既人就會有一堆五毛和應<br />\n之後就會順勢比關狗一齊打<br />\n結果就係反保皇狗既巴打就比佢話係五毛<br />\n今日關狗諗住開分身點知唔記得轉ac<br />\n<a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/593631/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/593631/page/1</a><br />\n雖然佢又話自嘲又成<br />\n係唔係想用分身開真係一睇就知<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但..一個恐怖既假設就出現<br />\n如果<br />\n果堆著名五毛原來就係佢既分身呢?<br />\n借住打五毛獲得信任<br />\n係補選時用呢點暗助保皇狗<br />\n一有人反保皇狗<br />\n佢就開埋分身去支持<br />\n再用佢關狗打五毛既身份連同反保皇狗既巴打一齊打呢?<br />\n要知道就算佢打一千一萬個五毛<br />\n都唔及影響一個議席來得緊要<br />\n係咪就解得通佢一直口講泛民保皇一樣<br />\n但一直只追屌泛民放生保皇<br />\n大家可以諗諗<br />\n<br />\n証明1：<br />\n五毛狙擊手 &bull; 5d<br />\n<a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/597048/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/597048/page/1</a><br />\n一屌保皇狗<br />\n例牌又係入來用泛民轉移視線<br />\n<br />\n証明2：<br />\n証明2:<a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/575599/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/575599/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"a36d574db7134720d5be12c319e363a3e8635e24","tid":607252,"uid":38523,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T06:56:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/607167/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/607167/page/1</a><br />\n明明應緊關愛座<br />\n個河本鬼茂冇啦啦又代關狗應？<br />\n係咪又唔記得轉ac 呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n轉個頭又話我係泛民打手<br />\n但關狗之前先屌人反問反泛民就係保皇打手？<br />\n呢班人兩個玩法<br />\n西利西利"},{"pid":"c02c96329161f1386d0c6a4e38175901944f9684","tid":607252,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T06:58:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b0441a842537f78169c67627808f3b66d611bf15","tid":607252,"uid":86557,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T06:58:46.000Z","msg":"關我撚事？"},{"pid":"c37d94902883bf29e596e124d82f4b1668ebda3a","tid":607252,"uid":27451,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b0441a842537f78169c67627808f3b66d611bf15","tid":607252,"uid":86557,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T06:58:46.000Z","msg":"關我撚事？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T07:09:28.000Z","msg":"x 2"},{"pid":"7bb2c0a5ec756e5edd2428f9741c6f23490490ca","tid":607252,"uid":99364,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T07:16:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c209236cfe9fab5c6a34c3796d959896634f2ed8","tid":607252,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T07:58:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"590e7b9aa3011146314775d497c17d56e814b86d","tid":607252,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T07:59:55.000Z","msg":"不如你哋停火啦"},{"pid":"86fe61eb636e6e43cfd10efe757973b69d3a9ab5","tid":607252,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T08:14:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f2a8943f56659073f1c977c9b277b24cad185bb8","tid":607252,"uid":27451,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"86fe61eb636e6e43cfd10efe757973b69d3a9ab5","tid":607252,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"590e7b9aa3011146314775d497c17d56e814b86d","tid":60725